Rip notes: nothing was ripped

Indulge yourself in a totally new concept, created by Sega for its online gaming world. It's an online Theme Park, containing many exciting elements ; there are currently 4 mini attractions on this planet, each is simple but addictive : Dream Dorobo, Ball bubble, SOAR and Splash.
Together with other amenities such as RING Messenger and many entertaining events to be introduced in the future, this is truly a gamers paradize! Online gaming available in UK, France, Germany, Spain, Italy and Ireland.